%h3
  Adding Frameworks to Compass

%ul
  %li
    Add a folder under
    %code
      compass/frameworks
  %li
    Register it by creating a file in
    %code
      compass/lib/compass/frameworks/
  %li
    Require it in
    %code
      compass/lib/compass/frameworks.rb
    \.

